title: Kemono Kingdom: Zoo
sinopse:
King Panda is dead and the Upper Yard of the Zoo is left without a ruler. The animals of the East jockey for domination while the peaceful animals of the West prepare for the oncoming war. It's the cutest and funniest animal civil war you'll ever see!

(Source: MU)

Included one-shot:
Volume 1: Hadaka Muffler
